{"tid":60574,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[檔案歷史]英國戴卓爾解密原始檔案","createTime":"2016-12-30T14:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T14:21:26.000Z","uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f01822713844284db3155b82e06d09d2347fc2","tid":60574,"uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"From 世代懺悔錄 <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1758851027770281&amp;id=1662302910758427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1758851027770281%26id%3D1662302910758427&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=a5741dd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1758851027770281&amp;id=1662302910758427</a><br />\n<br />\n[#考古現場 005]<br />\n今早兩份港媒報導英國檔案處最新解封檔案，揭露六四屠殺後的中港政局，主要資料來自戴卓爾基金會網站。該網站收錄戴卓爾當政時各式檔案密件，大部分已解密又處理好的都有PDF，普通人坐喺屋企都可睇到。<br />\n<br />\n聯合聲明前後較重要的主題，多數已被主流媒體報導。經過他們導賞，自己再原汁原味睇原始檔案文獻，既可培養歷史感，亦可更了解當中細節，有助發掘更多被忽略主題。<br />\n<br />\n這裡以最新解封檔案為例，示範基本玩法，最起碼可以利用檔案搜尋器打keyword：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.margaretthatcher.org/archive/search.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.margaretthatcher.org%2Farchive%2Fsearch.asp&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2a661f0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.margaretthatcher.org/archive/search.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n1) 搜尋&quot;Hong Kong&quot;會出現一千多項資料，關於1989年的最新檔案註有&quot;[declassified 2016]&quot;。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.margaretthatcher.org/archive/results.asp?ps=500&amp;w=Hong%20AND%20Kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.margaretthatcher.org%2Farchive%2Fresults.asp%3Fps%3D500%26w%3DHong%2520AND%2520Kong&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=5c7586c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.margaretthatcher.org/archive/results.asp?ps=500&amp;w=Hong%20AND%20Kong</a><br />\n<br />\n2) 打開其中一項，是英駐新加坡高級專員向外交及聯邦事務部(FCO)電報報告，與李光耀通電話談六四後中港局勢，文件可以獨立下載。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.margaretthatcher.org/document/149488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.margaretthatcher.org%2Fdocument%2F149488&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=5fb2f197\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.margaretthatcher.org/document/149488</a><br />\n<br />\n3) 想睇哂全個file原件，可以在Editorial comments找註有&quot;The full file from which this item is taken can be seen here&quot;的連結，自己下載。裡面有更豐富材料，是FCO自1979年5月至1989年7月關於中國的檔案，REM19/2597 f9就是掃描檔第九版。<br />\n<br />\n4) 至於其他香港前途的原件files，可以在Archive主頁連結去download PM's files，搜尋&quot;Hong Kong&quot;去找。最主要是註明&quot;Future of Hong Kong&quot;的檔案，共18卷，其他也是與香港有關事務。這批檔案照計都應在2014年底解封，但實際上仍有被政府暫時收起的。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.margaretthatcher.org/archive/PREM19_list7984.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.margaretthatcher.org%2Farchive%2FPREM19_list7984.asp&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=d589a7e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.margaretthatcher.org/archive/PREM19_list7984.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n5) 檔案搜尋器還可以找人物，譬如找包玉剛&quot;Y. K. Pao&quot;(Person's Name)，最早記錄是1979年5月。<br />\n<br />\n話說1982年戴卓爾訪京後抵港，包玉剛向她秘密傳話透露鄧小平隨時打算強硬接收香港執平貨，文件可以在1982年9月28日的<br />\nHong Kong: No.10 record of conversation (MT, Yue-Kong Pao: &ldquo;Hong Kong: Sir Y.K. Pao&rdquo;) [future of Hong Kong]，即PREM19/788 f46找到。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.margaretthatcher.org/archive/results.asp?ps=500&amp;w=%22Y%20K%20Pao%22&amp;scope=names\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.margaretthatcher.org%2Farchive%2Fresults.asp%3Fps%3D500%26w%3D%2522Y%2520K%2520Pao%2522%26scope%3Dnames&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=67cc1676\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.margaretthatcher.org/archive/results.asp?ps=500&amp;w=%22Y%20K%20Pao%22&amp;scope=names</a><br />\n<br />\n其他玩法，各位有興趣可自行探索！<br />\n<br />\n-- 材料豐富，歡迎分享，在專頁按Liked &gt;See First會送埋上門 --<br />\n<br />\n#基本玩法 #戴卓爾基金會"},{"pid":"e27b499931954cd632b41199921207cccefdf2a5","tid":60574,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6d653fc749f47dc8757ce53a021f96478e5978","tid":60574,"uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:21:04.000Z","msg":"這篇報導反映，當時中共真係幾熬底<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161230/56108177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161230%2F56108177&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=3163714d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161230%2F56108177&h=b71fc818\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161230/56108177</a>"},{"pid":"f7eb1fcb073e712439f8164e268dff7cc0a47df3","tid":60574,"uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:21:26.000Z","msg":"關於最新解封檔案與未解封檔案消息<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161230/s00001/1483034428642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161230%2Fs00001%2F1483034428642&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA0wT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=0abeca3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161230%2Fs00001%2F1483034428642&h=a850a76c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161230/s00001/1483034428642</a>"}]}